es and problem-solving skills to progress through three demo levels, collecting lost gift packages and stamps along the way. With your wits and stilts, you can handle any challenge: pass chasms, avoid traps, break things and smack creatures. \n\nThe full version features:\n* hours more of singleplayer levels\n* more power-ups\n* various multiplayer game modes\n* cross-play with Quest, PCVR and PSVR2 players!\n\nGet the full version of Stilt here! https://www.meta.com/experiences/app/5632444056884139/", "short_description": "A VR platformer with unique movement, inspired by classic platformers. Arm yourself with stilts and use your quick reflexes and problem-solving skills to complete levels!\n(This is a demo version of the game.)"}]}, "developer_name": "Rekt Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/stilt-privacy-notice", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MeKiwi", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://stiltgame.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ADVENTURE", "ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7632636206797244"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974491_863292728446922_7903663429858675821_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nsN